OVERVIEW
========
   Other topics
DESCRIPTION
===========
   This directory collects a variety of topics relevant to programming and 
   maintaining an LDMud.

   - driver
   - efuns
   - External Request Demon
   - files
   - Henry Spencer Regular Expressions
   - InterMUD Message Protocol
   - inheritance
   - variable initialization
   - Intermud communication
   - intermud.basic
   - lfuns
   - limitations
   - The Mud Client Compression Protocol
   - memory swapping
   - mysql
   - `native` driver mode
   - Telnet Negotiations
   - objects
   - overloading
   - Perl-compatible regular expressions
   - PostgreSQL support
   - Driver-defined preprocessor macros
   - Regular Expressions
   - The simul_efun object
   - telnet
   - transport layer security
   - userids

